title: Bug 121170: get column label from meta data object should return some user recognizable strings
OB: The labels returned before extraction are null, while the ones after extraction are recognizable strings.
EB: The 'get column label' function should return user recognizable strings both before and after extraction.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Perform an extraction using the meta data object. 
2. Retrieve the column labels before extraction using the 'get column label' function. 
3. Compare the retrieved labels with the recognizable strings obtained after extraction using the same function.
